{"tid":1157906,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"可憐貓貓狗狗需要關注","createTime":"2019-05-16T15:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T15:14:00.000Z","uid":245259,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42db828f78d804a139426abf465ee5c86b150410","tid":1157906,"uid":245259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:08:52.000Z","msg":"今時今日，香港仍有不少被遺棄或者在街頭流浪的貓貓狗狗身處在收容所中，這一類的貓貓狗狗的數目正在逐漸增加中，收容所的經濟負擔和人手壓力也正在加劇中。如果將貓狗共享的概論應用在貓狗收容所上，再加上一些對收養者的審查，從而確保貓狗的安全。那麼分享一隻收容所的貓狗似乎是個好主意。它可以讓狗狗走出收容所，享受一些樂趣和社交，並可能導致永久收養。<br />\n<br />\nbloglink<br />\n<a href=\"https://blog.ulifestyle.com.hk/blogger/sharedpets201819/2019/04/%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E6%94%B6%E5%AE%B9%E6%89%80%E7%9A%84%E8%B2%93%E8%B2%93%E7%8B%97%E7%8B%97/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblog.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fblogger%2Fsharedpets201819%2F2019%2F04%2F%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25BA%25AB%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%25AE%25B9%25E6%2589%2580%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B2%2593%25E8%25B2%2593%25E7%258B%2597%25E7%258B%2597%2F&d=nKoZ4xrs0zkQ%2F022jTHdf7V8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=ed80a9c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://blog.ulifestyle.com.hk/blogger/sharedpets201819/2019/04/%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%E6%94%B6%E5%AE%B9%E6%89%80%E7%9A%84%E8%B2%93%E8%B2%93%E7%8B%97%E7%8B%97/</a>"},{"pid":"c520a964b2834f903a77dab4c0835ec0703b4971","tid":1157906,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:14:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}